{"type": "article", "id": 23280, "title": "极简概念灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-04T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121218SVwY8Tsmoc9LzW6A.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一盏极为简化的灯，它近似一个圆筒一样的水杯，上面连接的手提带增加了它的便捷性。这盏灯通过太阳能发电，而可触式玻璃才是它真正的开关。灯的下面其实是一个音响，灯内的蓝牙系统可以连接到手机 app 以播放音乐。产品目前还是一个概念，<a href=\"http://alexandermain.com/#/sollys/\">这里是更多信息</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121215Xesa4O2DtJyoVQuj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121216AyGeumbHvZwqN34R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121216iIMo3X7n86fkqltc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121217ChPfZATF9kSW12Mc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121217Peb5rRv8H7qoxID2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}